as such as OAuth2 helpers or POJO databind may require optional/test-only dependencies, but they are not required for meaningful core coverage.\",\n    \"The reported failure includes Netty native-image runtime connection resets caused by `PlatformDependent0.safeConstructPutInt`, so local Gradle and Native Image verification should confirm the system-property fix.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0289a7f098fbcc8a016a40e4ede79c8195aa3156ceb27a23ec\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 3940, "output": 607, "cacheRead": 29184, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 33731, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782637798262, "responseId": "resp_0289a7f098fbcc8a016a40e4e6d98881958f996dcb44f64aab"}, "toolResults": []}
